    <section id="Newcomer-Section">
      <h3 class="fs-5 header">Newcomer section</h3>
      <p>Oh look, a new recruit, <b>WELCOME!</b> I'm going to be your instructor today. My name is <span class="tip">Myndi</span>, and will do my best to squeeze the best out of you 😤 Nice to meet you!</p>
      <p>First things first, one of the most important things as a new player is to read. Perhaps not all the people like reading, even this paragraph will be skipped by a lot of them 😞 but that can't stop us from learning, and teaching them. <b>Let's jump right into the first thing you need to know!</b></p>

      <h4 id="Tutorial" class="header fs-6">Tutorial</h4>
      <p><span class="tag">DO NOT SKIP</span> Every great story starts with a tutorial. It might be tedious, but it's your mom, and she popping some mommy milkers 🧐 jokes aside, it's quite important, because this leads you to your next route.</p>

      <p>After finishing your tasks with mom, you're left with few options:</p>
      <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li class="ps-3"><b>a.</b> <span class="header">Continue on your own</span> - Essentially live up the original Ragnarok experience. You can adjust your experience <span class="low-focus">(you can only lower it down, not increase)</span> at <code class="code contrast">@go office</code> walking to the left and talking to <span class="tip">Eden Officer Eve</span>. There's nothing much I can add here, besides making sure you look at the map to see what places you could level up at.</li>
        <li class="ps-3"><b>b.</b> <span class="header">Follow Mom</span> - She will kindly ask you to join Eden Academy. You could do by going <code class="code contrast">@go eden</code> walk upwards and talk with <span class="tip">Secretary Lime Evenor</span>. You will be given a <img src="https://www.novaragnarok.com/data/items/icons2/6219.png" alt="Ragnarok Online item" class="item"> <span class="tip">Eden Group Mark</span> and a <img src="https://www.novaragnarok.com/data/items/icons2/34806.png" alt="Ragnarok Online item"> <span class="tip">Eden Equipment Chest</span> if successfully joined.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>With that in hand, we can jump into the next one.</p>

      <h4 id="Eden-Academy" class="header fs-6">Eden Academy</h4>
      <p><a href="https://www.novaragnarok.com/wiki/Eden_Academy" target="_blank" class="link">Eden Academy</a> is a follow up to the tutorial - if you want to read more about it, kindly do so.</p>
      <p>What is important here, is what they teach you, and the gear we acquire. From level <span class="number">0</span> to <span class="number">100</span> we will be using the set they provide us after we register to the Academy.</p>
    
      
