            <li><a href="https://www.novaragnarok.com/wiki/Refinement_System" target="_blank" class="link">Refinement System</a> - Frankly the best place to understand how refinement works.</li>
            <li><a href="https://www.novaragnarok.com/wiki/Creation_Database" target="_blank" class="link">Creation Database</a> - We all make potions or runes, and this place has it all.</li>
            <li><a href="https://www.novaragnarok.com/wiki/Pet_System" target="_blank" class="link">Pet System</a> - Always a good thing to have all the available pets.</li>
            <li><a href="https://www.novaragnarok.com/wiki/Palette_Colors" target="_blank" class="link">Outfit Colors</a> - Fashion is part of the game, so might as well have it recommended.</li>
